            "label": "Deploy ZooKeeper Ensemble HA node",
            "command": "set -euo pipefail\nlog() { printf '[zookeeper_ensemble_ha] %s\\n' \"$*\"; }\ndocker compose -f /opt/octastack/zookeeper_ensemble_ha/compose.yml pull\ndocker compose -f /opt/octastack/zookeeper_ensemble_ha/compose.yml up -d\ndocker compose -f /opt/octastack/zookeeper_ensemble_ha/compose.yml ps\n      log \"node deployment complete\"\n",
            "sudo": true
          }
        },
        {
          "id": "node_step_4",
          "type": "configCommandNode",
          "position": {
            "x": 1740,
            "y": 6215
          },
          "data": {
            "label": "Document ZooKeeper Ensemble HA topology",
            "command": "set -euo pipefail\ncat >/tmp/zookeeper_ensemble_ha-topology.md <<'EOF'\n# ZooKeeper Ensemble HA\n\nMembers:\n- zookeeper-01: 10.0.162.11 (zookeeper)\n- zookeeper-02: 10.0.162.12 (zookeeper)\n- zookeeper-03: 10.0.162.13 (zookeeper)\n\nThree ZooKeeper members form an odd-number ensemble with generated server IDs and peer addresses.\nEOF\ncat /tmp/zookeeper_ensemble_ha-topology.md\n",
            "sudo": true
          }
        },
